      "Installs and uses the inference.sh belt CLI.",
      "Discovers available AI apps by category, search term, or featured status.",
      "Runs image, video, LLM, search, audio, 3D, and utility apps.",
      "Generates sample input files and checks remote task status.",
      "Uploads local files when an app input accepts file paths.",
      "Provides references for authentication, app discovery, execution, and CLI commands."
